epoch.description: Time interval in which data is collected. Data is recorded at specific intervals (for example, every 10 minute)

weight__kg_.description: Weight of the individual in kilograms.

age.description: Age of the individual in years

kcals.description: Calories burned during the recorded period.

mets.description: Metabolic Equivalent of Task (MET), which measures the intensity of physical activity. (1 MET is the energy expenditure at rest)

freedson__1998__bouts.description: Reference to Freedson 1998 method for categorizing physical activity into bouts or episodes.

total_time_in_freedson__1998__bo.description: Total time in episodes of physical activity according to method Freedson 1998.

avg_time_per_freedson__1998__bou.description: Average time per episode of physical activity according to the Freedson 1998 method

max_time_per_freedson__1998__bou.description: Maximum time per episode of physical activity according to the Freedson 1998 method.

min_time_per_freedson__1998__bou.description: Minimum time per episode of physical activity according to the Freedson 1998 method.

total_counts_in_freedson__1998__.description: Total movement counts during bouts of physical activity according to the Freedson 1998 method

total_time_in_sedentary_bouts.description: Total time in episodes of sedentary time.

average_length_of_sedentary_bout.description: Average length of sedentary time episodes.

maximum_length_of_sedentary_bout.description: Maximum length of sedentary time episodes.

minimum_length_of_sedentary_bout.description: Minimum length of sedentary time episodes.

daily_average_of_sedentary_bouts.description: Daily average of episodes of sedentary time.

total_sedentary_breaks.description: Total interruptions in episodes of sedentary time

total_time_in_sedentary_breaks.description: Total time in interruptions during sedentary time.

average_length_of_sedentary_brea.description: Average length of interruptions in sedentary time.

max_length_of_sedentary_breaks.description: Maximum length of breaks in sedentary time

minimum_length_of_sedentary_brea.description: Minimum length of breaks in sedentary time.

daily_average_of_sedentary_break.description: Average daily interruptions in sedentary time.

very_vigorous.description: Total time in very vigorous activity.

___in_sedentary.description: Time in a sedentary state during the specified period

___in_light.description: Time in light activity during the specified period.

___in_moderate.description: Time in moderate activity during the specified period.

___in_vigorous.description: Time in vigorous activity during the specified period.

___in_very_vigorous.description: Time spent in very vigorous activity during the specified period

total_mvpa.description: Total time in moderate to vigorous physical activity (MVPA).

___in_mvpa.description: Time spent in moderate to vigorous physical activity during the specified period

average_mvpa_per_day.description: Average daily time spent in moderate to vigorous physical activity.

axis_1_counts.description: Counting of movements in axis 1 of the accelerometer.

axis_2_counts.description: Counting movements in axis 2 of the accelerometer.

axis_3_counts.description: Counting movements in axis 3 of the accelerometer.

vector_magnitude_counts.description: Counts based on acceleration vector magnitude

vector_magnitude_average_counts.description: Average count based on the magnitude of the acceleration vector

vector_magnitude_max_counts.description: Maximum count based on the magnitude of the acceleration vector

vector_magnitude_cpm.description: Counts per minute based on the magnitude of the acceleration vector

steps_average_counts.description: Average step count per minute or hour

steps_max_counts.description: Maximum step count in a period

lux_average_counts.description: Average lux (illumination) levels during the period

number_of_epochs.description: Total number of time intervals in the data set.

calendar_days.description: Total number of calendar days in the study or measurement period
